Preheat oven to 350 degrees F. Empty spinach into a large colander. Pour boiling water over the spinach until wilted. Squeeze the spinach to remove excess moisture; place on cutting board and coarsely chop. Mix remaining ingredients in large bowl. Stir in spinach. Spoon into greased 1-quart baking dish. Bake 25 to 30 min. or until heated through.